              "message": "D2 decides that the syn walker recursively visits every generic argument without container special cases, so a type like `MyContainer<String>` should already be detected the same way as `Vec<String>`. The Reassess trigger here says custom generic containers are outside the current detectable set and may need future support, which contradicts D1/D2 and leaves downstream spec/type work unsure whether to implement a whitelist of known transparent containers or a true full recursive TypeRef walk.",
