            {
              "message": "`task-coverage.json` omits `CN-02` entirely, even though T001 explicitly treats \"The domain crate must gain no syn dependency (CN-02)\" as a load-bearing constraint. That leaves the no-`syn` invariant untracked in the coverage artifact while adjacent constraints (`CN-01`, `CN-03`..`CN-09`) are mapped.",
